      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PYRENEES ACE (3) was in the minors two back (23.35) at this track but ran below best last time there, finishing 6th. Form here at the trip sound including seven wins. Comes out of a solid form race last start. Worth another chance. BREAKN' A SWEAT (2) is a capable type and proved too classy last time to win by 1.75 lengths at Bendigo in a handy 24.11 beating Paw Prydi. Has hit winning form and can go on with it. PAW JESSABELLE (1) has a strong record this journey here with two wins and a minor from five starts. Missed the frame latest (24.48) when seventh over 410m at this track in a Special conditions race. Can feature in the finish. PAW DROGO (6) gets a chance to improve on an unplaced run at his latest outing at this circuit.",
